TapStyle for Hair Salon (Business)

TapStyle for Hair Salon 3.6.1

Device: iOS Universal

Category: Business

Price: Free, Version: 3.6.0 -> 3.6.1 (iTunes)

Description:

TapStyle makes your hair salon/beauty salon business more efficient and stylish. TapStyle offers all the necessary features for hair salon / hair stylist / hairdresser in one package.

Features

- Booking / Schedule management

- Customer management

- Service Record Log (with photo)

- POS (Point of sales) / Gift Voucher / Receipt / Credit Card Reader integration

- Inventory Management

- Catalog

- Business Analysis / Graphical Statistics

- Booking Reminder / Confirmation message

- Direct Mail Marketing

- Visualized customer referral relations

- Accounting (profit review, book keeping, expense management, flexible tax rate)

- Staff commission management

- Reporting

- Automatic data backup

- Data synchronisation among multiple devices

- Online booking

Let's make your hair salon STYLISH!

TapStyle can download and use it for free, so please try by all means first.

In addition, the monthly subscription license (‘TapStyle monthly subscription', $14 per month) is available via in-app purchase to access to the full features and unlimited data storing. Subscriptions will be charged to your credit card through your iTunes account. Your subscription will automatically renew unless turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. You can manage your subscriptions in the Account Settings after purchase. Please refer http://www.tapstyle.net/privacy.html for the privacy policy.

If you have any questions or requests, please contact us via support site.

What's New

- Fixed the issue that the photo was not shown on selecting goods on checkout.

Device: iOS Universal

Category: Navigation

Price: Free, Version: 11.0.0 -> 11.1.1 (iTunes)

Description:

BIXI is the official mobile application for Montreal’s bike sharing system.

Bikemap - Map for Cycling (Healthcare & Fitness)

Bikemap - Map for Cycling 10.2.2

Device: iOS Universal

Category: Healthcare & Fitness

Price: Free, Version: 10.2.1 -> 10.2.2 (iTunes)

Description:

You love to discover, navigate and record new bike routes? No matter if you're riding a mountain bike, cross bike, e-bike or road bike - the free Bikemap app helps you navigate the latest and greatest cycling paths - voice navigation included.

• Explore more than 3.5M bike routes worldwide

• Discover amazing national & international cycling regions

• Get personalized cycling route recommendations

• Use the latest cycling navigation technology

• Navigate user routes, including voice instructions

• Personal tracking with the Bikemap app for Apple Watch and Apple Health integration

• Track your best cycling tours (GPX & KML support)

• Share your personal progress with your friends and use the Bikemap iMessage extension to send routes directly from within iMessage

• Save cycling routes and maps offline (premium)

DISCOVER THE MOST BEAUTIFUL CYCLING ROUTES

Find more than 3.5M bike routes worldwide. Discover beautiful cycling regions for your next bike trip - whether in your home country or abroad. Get useful information, such as route length and an interactive elevation profile, for every cycling route. Every day, thousands of exciting new bicycle routes are added by our active community.

GET PERSONALISED BIKE ROUTE RECOMMENDATIONS

Personalize your next cycling trip according to your desired elevation profile. The Bikemap cycling navigation is designed to continually learn to give you personalized bike route recommendations. Even in unknown places you cycle like a local and are always on the right bike track. Navigate routes recorded by other users or nearby friends, directly on your mountain bike, race bike or cross bike.

USE THE LATEST CYCLING NAVIGATION TECHNOLOGY

With the Bikemap cycling navigation you safely track from A to B - worldwide. When off the bike path, the intelligent routing system brings you back onto the cycling route. Use the app as your bike computer or tachometer and see route information, like distance and elevation profile, in real-time. Voice-enabled turn by turn directions give you accurate instructions on your next bike tour.

ENHANCE YOUR PERSONAL CYCLING PROFILE

Save your favourite cycling trips and create the ultimate route collection. Your activity is tracked and saved automatically, so you have all the insights on distance covered, average and top speed as well as ascent and descent of your recent bike rides. The Bikemap app also automatically integrates with Apple Health.

SHARE YOUR BIKE TOUR EXPERIENCES WITH FRIENDS

Bikemap enables a community of more than 1M enthusiastic cyclists to digitally enhance their favourite sport. Add photos or points of interest to your cycling routes and share them directly with your biking friends. Stay up to date about your personal cycling community and get motivated for new personal bests!

BIKEMAP PREMIUM - TRY 7 DAYS FOR FREE

With an upgrade to a Bikemap Premium, you gain access to exclusive features. Payment will be charged to your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase. The monthly subscription is $4.99 per month, while the yearly subscription is $29.99 per year (price may vary by location). Your free trial subscription will automatically renew to a paid subscription / your subscription renews automatically unless cancelled at least 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. Any unused free trial time will be forfeited when purchasing premium.

You can cancel your Bikemap Premium membership to the end of the current period by turning off Auto-renewal in your iTunes account settings after purchase. You can also manage your subscriptions in Account Settings after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active subscription period.

Terms of use: https://www.bikemap.net/terms-of-service

Privacy policy: https://www.bikemap.net/dataprivacy

What's New

• New: We lubricated the chain and Bikemap launches super-fast now!

• New: Bikemap is now GDPR-compliant.

• Lots of other improvements and bug fixes.

We hope that you'll have great cycling experiences with the new Bikemap. We are looking forward to your feedback, so shoot us a message to support@bikemap.net.

Let's keep making the app better together – and make sure to give us five stars!

Happy cycling!

Bikemap - Map for Cycling

Category: Books

Aplikasi Toko Buku adalah sebuah aplikasi yang berisi kumpulan buku-buku digital dengan berbagai tema pilihan bacaan. Aplikasi Toko Buku merupakan aplikasi yang mengisyaratkan kepraktisan dan kemudahan dalam membeli dan membaca buku secara modern, terjangkau dan bisa menyimpan begitu banyak buku dalam satu teknologi.

Kami percaya bahwa kehadiran buku konvensional akan tetap menjadi produk yang akan terus ada, tapi kami lebih percaya bahwa buku elektronik akan semakin berkembang dengan seiringnya waktu. Hal ini bisa dibuktikan, bahwa dengan menggunakan buku elektronik, biaya produksi dan harga jualnya yang akan jauh lebih terjangkau dari sebuah buku cetak.

Aplikasi Toko Buku bisa di download secara gratis di iPad, iPhone dan iPod touch, dan siap menampung dan menjual berbagai karya dari penulis yang ingin mempromosikan tulisan mereka secara digital, dan bisa di download di Apps Store sehingga bisa diakses dengan mudah kapanpun dan dimanapun.

Keunggulan Toko Buku:

- Berisi kumpulan berbagai macam tema buku: buku sastra, buku ilmiah, buku resep masakan, buku agama, buku anak, buku pendidikan, buku motivasi dan pengembangan diri, dll

- Terhubung dengan Majalah Indonesia

- Setiap buku dalam kategori akan terus bertambah seiring berjalannya waktu

Mahoni.com menerima semua buku yang bisa ditampilkan di Toko Buku dan siap untuk di jual. Siapkan karya-karya anda untuk di tampilkan dan di jual, serta bergabung menjadi partner Mahoni.com untuk mengisi Toko Buku dengan berbagai buku-buku menarik lainnya dengan banyak tema dan kategori.

With this solitaire game you get unlimited puzzle games, all free games, all best of class games, and we have added a Smart Point System and multiple levels of difficulty: Easy, Medium, and Hard :)

With our auto-hint activate, as long as the game is solvable, you will never feel stuck in the game!

• klondike solitaire game rules

Card Games solitaire is an iPhone game and an iPad game combined into one iOS app. Your iPhone, iPod, or iPad automatically selects for you the iPhone app and iPad app.

Card Games solitaire is part of our family of card games and puzzle games, all created with the same mix of passion for enjoyment, midnight oil, and deep technology skills to bring you the best solitaires… try the difference!

The feeling of playing Solitaire is not just that of playing cards… it's the feeling of being part of a community… an enriching, shared experience that never makes you feel apart!

The concept of FruVeg was born from the passion we have to lead a healthy life. By having quality fruits and vegetables delivered directly to your home or business, you are one step closer to living healthier and with less hassle.

Our main business priority is to provide customer satisfaction and this concept is incorporated in the manner in which we operate our company. Simply sign up as a member and you will have access to a wide array of produce of your choosing at your fingertips. As a method to guaranteeing your complete satisfaction, payment for your purchase will only be accepted after inspecting the items purchased at the time of delivery.

GUÍA COMERCIAL

Una guía que hará más fácil sus compras. Comercios organizados por categorías y búsquedas filtradas con las que encontrar más fácil y rápido todo aquello que busca, además de una completa ficha técnica, con todos los datos que pueda necesitar, incluyendo ofertas y descuentos de cada comercio, distancia a la que se encuentran de usted, horarios o formas de contacto, pudiendo crear fácilmente su propia lista de favoritos.

GUÍA TURISTICA

Una completa guía turística del municipio que reúne toda la información que pueda necesitar durante su visita: dónde ir, qué ver, que comer, un poco de historia y costumbres, y las fiestas más importantes del municipio, todo ello acompañado de planos que le harán más cómoda su visita.

CUIDANDO LO NUESTRO

Una novedosa herramienta puesta en las manos de la ciudadanía para la comunicación de incidencias, averías o desperfectos que se hayan producido en los espacios públicos, mobiliario o equipamiento urbano, y que nos ayude en la mejora de nuestro municipio. Tan solo tomando una foto y enviándola, la etiqueta de geolocalización de la imagen nos dirá donde ha sido tomada y nos ayudará a ponerle solución lo antes posible.
